*Writing directly to <<<HttpServletResponse>>>

  Declaring <<<HttpServletResponse>>> as a method parameter gives direct control over status codes,
  response headers, and the output stream.  When writing directly to the response, do not also
  declare an <<<ObjectResponse>>> parameter — the framework assumes one or the other:

